{"tid":2507432,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"林祖舜將高登公海會員正式會員化都冇人講?","createTime":"2021-04-28T04:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T07:23:47.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2c0cd5cc3bbc833722b3804d201db054d66fbb","tid":2507432,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:01:44.000Z","msg":"致各位公海會員 :<br />\n<br />\n你好，經過高登管理團隊決定，我們會將一些對高登討論區有貢獻的公海會員升級為正式會員。<br />\n<br />\n經甄選後，我們決定升級閣下為正常會員並即日生效，如有任何問題歡迎向我們查詢。<br />\n<br />\n除此以外，我們最近因加強封禁公海五毛，有會員回報被無故封禁，我們已解封相關帳號，如你受到相關影響，我們就此致歉。<br />\n<br />\n高登引入香討式藍絲入去 正式成為中立論壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8e4a9a9007097174198ecc67234748e8d5f70a","tid":2507432,"uid":886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:02:35.000Z","msg":"咩係公海會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d2a7fff768073bcd2331fcceeec8ce2b866ce1","tid":2507432,"uid":388757,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:02:43.000Z","msg":"乜撚野係公海會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06f527a7938fa91b803557d9bb563c66c943c82","tid":2507432,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"好耐冇login過<br />\n上去睇下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649540ef5a00544b78e0f0785758472d10e2ae6f","tid":2507432,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a5d2a7fff768073bcd2331fcceeec8ce2b866ce1","tid":2507432,"uid":388757,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:02:43.000Z","msg":"乜撚野係公海會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\